#. <section class="sutta" id="sn47.33"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn47.33:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 47"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 47"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.33:0.2"
msgid "4. Ananussutavagga"
msgstr "4. Not Learned From Anyone Else"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn47.33:0.3"
msgid "33. Viraddhasutta"
msgstr "33. Missed Out"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.180"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: viraddho tesaṃ ariyo maggo → ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo (s1-3, mr)
msgctxt "sn47.33:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Yesaṃ kesañci, bhikkhave, cattāro satipaṭṭhānā viraddhā, viraddho tesaṃ "
"ariyo maggo sammā dukkhakkhayagāmī."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, whoever has missed out on the four kinds of mindfulness "
"meditation has missed out on the noble path to the complete ending of "
"suffering."

msgctxt "sn47.33:1.2"
msgid ""
"Yesaṃ kesañci, bhikkhave, cattāro satipaṭṭhānā āraddhā, āraddho tesaṃ ariyo "
"maggo sammā dukkhakkhayagāmī."
msgstr ""
"Whoever has undertaken the four kinds of mindfulness meditation has "
"undertaken the noble path to the complete ending of suffering."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn47.33:2.1"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn47.33:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kāye kāyānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā, "
"vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant meditates by observing an aspect of the body—keen, "
"aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world."

msgctxt "sn47.33:2.3"
msgid "vedanāsu … pe …"
msgstr "They meditate observing an aspect of feelings …"

msgctxt "sn47.33:2.4"
msgid "citte … pe …"
msgstr "mind …"

msgctxt "sn47.33:2.5"
msgid ""
"dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke "
"abhijjhādomanassaṃ."
msgstr ""
"principles—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the "
"world."

msgctxt "sn47.33:2.6"
msgid ""
"Yesaṃ kesañci, bhikkhave, ime cattāro satipaṭṭhānā viraddhā, viraddho tesaṃ "
"ariyo maggo sammā dukkhakkhayagāmī."
msgstr ""
"Whoever has missed out on these four kinds of mindfulness meditation has "
"missed out on the noble path to the complete ending of suffering."

msgctxt "sn47.33:2.7"
msgid ""
"Yesaṃ kesañci, bhikkhave, ime cattāro satipaṭṭhānā āraddhā, āraddho tesaṃ "
"ariyo maggo sammā dukkhakkhayagāmī”ti."
msgstr ""
"Whoever has undertaken these four kinds of mindfulness meditation has "
"undertaken the noble path to the complete ending of suffering.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn47.33:2.8"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
